"{\"uid\": \"flotrack.org-articles-12755665-aau-junior-olympics-track-and-field-2024-results-on-day-4\", \"text\": \"Adidas Indoor Nationals  Redlands Invitational  Chandler Rotary Invite  Texas Distance Festival  Run Rome the Marathon  David Noble Relays  Emory Thrills in the Hills  WashU Distance Carnival  Jim Taylor Duals  Doc Jopson Invitational  2026 FSU Relays  Continental Tour: Maurie Plant Meet  WashU Invite  Monmouth Home Opener  Sunny skies are back in Greensboro, NC.  The 2024 AAU Junior Olympics kicked off day 4 out of eight starting with 1500m finals for ages 13 through 18.  11-year-old Andrew Francis set four national records in the high jump with his final record clearing 1.73m. Francis attempted to set a fifth national record at 1.76m, but scratched on all three of his attempts.  The 2024 Junior Olympics Track and Field competition isstreaming live on FloTrack, MileSplit and the FloSports app.Highlights, replays and breaking news are on both platforms.  Do not miss all the track and field season action streaming on FloTrack.Check out the FloTrack schedule for more events.  Video footage from each event will be archived and stored in a video library for FloTrack subscribers to watch for the duration of their subscriptions.  Tags:  Get the most important Track & Field stories delivered straight to your inbox.  \\u00a92006 - Present FloSports, Inc. All rights reserved.\"}"